  <brief_title>Post-exercise Insulin Reductions in Type 1 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Metabolic and Glycaemic Responses to Reductions in Rapid-acting Insulin Dose After Running Exercise in People With Type 1 Diabetes Mellitus.</official_title>
